reviewText: I've seen this entire 12 episode series online and, I've got to admit... it's phenomenal. This is really beautiful love story. I have only one gripe with it. I wish the soundtrack had more songs. Other than that, If you're really into love stories that you'll be emotionally invested in this [IS] that story. : )

STUNNING!
Flawless performances, especially Takeshi Kaneshiro.
Music was excellent, too
Absolutely first class production in every way.
This is one that will be watched over and over.

The quality of the video is good. Subtitles aren't that perfect. They keep saying him when they mean her. or the other way around. But other than that i'm perfectly content with the delivery, the product. The quick service! Excellent :)
